<p>Recently, a wise man encouraged me to aim higher. &#8220;What would you accomplish if you set out to 10x your productivity?&#8221;</p><p>Challenge accepted.</p><p>Goodbye, old pace of 4 books per decade. Hello, plan to release 4 books this year alone&#8212;without help from AI tools.</p><p>Since there&#8217;s nothing quite like a public commitment to light a fire under me, I&#8217;m introducing them now:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa109deca-d78f-4b22-acf5-477acb624203_1200x1200.jpeg" width="412" height="412" data-attrs="{&quot;src&qu